    <description>E.G.O from L-Corp\n"It feeds on the “evil” that seeps out during conversations between people." -One Sin and Hundreds of Good Deeds.</description>
    <graphicData>
      <texPath>Things/Item/Equipment/WeaponMelee/EGOOnesin</texPath>
